    &lt;p&gt;Hi! Welcome to my message bank. Please feel free to post a new message by clicking on the &lt;a href="{{ url_for('submit') }}"&gt;Post Messages&lt;/a&gt; link. You can also view some random messages from the bank by clicking &lt;a href="{{ url_for('view') }}"&gt;View Messages&lt;/a&gt;. Hope you enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;
