This section greats the user by welcoming them to the message bank and telling the user the options they can do from here.
We also create two links for the user “Post Messages” and “View Messages” that would lead to the submit and view routes respectively.
Therefore once a user chooses what they want to do they are redirected to the correct page.
We can also view the style.css file that I used for styling the base page:

